X. RIJCKLOFF VAN GOENS, CORNELIS SPEELMAN, BALTHASAR BORT, ANTHONIO HURDT, DIRCK BLOM, WILLEM VAN OUTHOORN EN JOANNES CAMPHUYS, BATAVIA 10 october 1679. 
